groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: DGT Hagley Museum
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description:
Location description.

Access from Old Barley Mill Road which is off of Rt 141.
This cache is only acessible 9:30 to 4:30 daily since it is inside the locked gates of the Hagley Grounds. Go through the gate to the visitor parking area.
